│     "old": "    SmallVector<int> SubVectorsMask(SubVector.size(), PoisonMaskElem);",       │
│     "new": "    SmallVector<int> SubVectorsMask(UniqueScalars.size(), PoisonMaskElem);"    │
│   }                                                                                        │
│ }                                                                                          │
│ </tool_call>                                                                               │
│ The edit has been applied. Now, I will run the tests to verify the fix.                    │
